{
  "text": "Doris and Dweck [CITATION_1] suggested that bioprosthetic valve degeneration may be triggered by a mechanism involving subclinical leaflet thrombosis and secondary calcification of the leaflets, leading to subsequent degenerative changes and valve dysfunction.",
